### creating user
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "gopi",
    "lastName": "more",
    "email": "gopimore@gmail.com",
    "password": "User@12345",
    "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/avatars/author.png"
}


### authenticating user
###
POST http://localhost:4000/common-api/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "gopimore@gmail.com",
    "password": "User@12345",
    "role":"USER"
}


