#### read the articles of a author
####
GET http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/698a90354ba0b500522dd8bc


#### update article by author
###
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "author":"698a90354ba0b500522dd8bc",
    "articleId":"698a90a64ba0b500522dd8c1",
     "title":"javaScript",
     "category":"Web Dev",
     "content":"content of javascript article"

}

